
-------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Used between services

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

4 Types:

1. Storage Queues
2. Event Grid
3. Service Bus
4. Event Hub

-------------------------------------------------------------------------

Storage Queue:
    
* Part of Storage Account

Event Grid:

* Event based architecture
* Event -> Event grid - Event Handler (ex: Functions)

Service Bus:

* Managed blown message queueing service
* Supports point-to-point (Queue) or pub/sub service (ex: event grid)

Event Hub:

* Big Data streaming platform
* Managed Kafka implementation
* Can recieve millions of events per minute

-------------------------------------------------------------------------